== uniCenta oPOS 2.53  ==



uniCenta oPOS is a Touchscreen Friendly Point of Sale application.

It supports screen resolutions from 800x600 pixels upwards; ESC/Java POS and SurePOS ticket printers; 2 line x 20chr per line Customer Displays; Magnetic Card Readers; Barcode Scanners and Weighing Scales.
It is also Multiuser (dependant on database used - Derby, mySQL; Postgres and Oracle) and includes Product and Customer maintenance forms, Reports including Charts.


You can access the latest Release Notes, Manuals and Installation instructions at;
http://www.unicentaopos.co.uk or http://www.unicenta.net/projects/unicentaopos/ or  http://www.sourceforge.net/projects/unicentaopos/


The latest version can be found at uniCenta's Sourceforge web site http://www.sourceforge.net/projects/unicentaopos



